data.title: Justin Moore and I Share The Same Favorite TV Show And Character
data.meta_description: Justin Moore's favorite is probably your favorite too
data.text:
The reasons why I love Justin Moore just keep piling on. He is a man that keeps it country. I feel confident saying you will never hear a Justin Moore songs on our sister station Kiss 95.1. He lives on part of his Granddad’s farm along with other extended family members and just found out we love the same television show.

Justin used to watch Westerns with his grandfather while growing up. He reportedly says he is a huge fan of Yellowstone

. We share the same character on the show too. We both love Beth.

Don’t you wish ladies you were as smart, beautiful and sassy as John Dutton’s only daughter. At least I do. Lets take a look at some of Beth’s best moments. WARNING: STRONG AND I MEAN STRONG LANGUAGE

Catherine Lane is the morning show co-host and midday host on Country 1037 in Charlotte, North Carolina. She has been with the station for the past 24 years and is a recipient of the Academy of Country Music Major Market Personality of the Year award. Catherine has been on air in both radio and television in the Queen City for 38 years. As a content creator for Country 1037, Catherine writes blogs on local events and restaurants. She also writes about great travel spots and out of the way places in the Carolinas. Anything outdoors, travel, food, animals or the many country artists from the Carolinas.
